JOHANNESBURG - ANC treasurer-general Zweli Mkhize told a business breakfast at the ANC National Policy Conference on Saturday that the government and the private sector needed to work together to grow the economy. #ANCNPC Mkhize: We must hunt as a pack as South Africa Inc. You can't hunt as a pack if you keep ownership white. This is the time to do it! For more on the morning's proceedings from reporter Michael Appel and analyst Angelo Fick, watch the video above. eNCA